2
00:00:19,480 --> 00:00:20,600
[sighs]

3
00:00:20,690 --> 00:00:21,730
[suspenseful music playing]

4
00:00:21,810 --> 00:00:22,980
So you're telling me,

5
00:00:23,070 --> 00:00:26,570
that this whole mess started with a virus
made by a high school science teacher?

6
00:00:31,620 --> 00:00:32,910
This virus.

7
