Tell me why?
Why would you do something like this?

8
00:00:36,500 --> 00:00:37,460
Detective.

9
00:00:40,880 --> 00:00:42,380
Do you have any kids?

10
00:00:43,210 --> 00:00:44,920
[kids clamoring]

11
00:00:45,800 --> 00:00:48,380
[Hee-su whimpering]

12
00:00:50,050 --> 00:00:50,890
[straining]

13
00:00:51,640 --> 00:00:53,220
[sobbing]

14
00:00:56,220 --> 00:00:57,480
[sobbing]

15
00:00:59,190 --> 00:01:01,560
[sobbing continues]

16
00:01:02,690 --> 00:01:04,770
-[baby cries]
-[Hee-su crying]

17
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:08,530
[baby crying]

18
00:01:08,610 --> 00:01:09,610
[breathing heavily]

19
00:01:10,110 --> 00:01:11,490
-[sniffles]
-[baby crying continues]

20
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:15,450
[Hee-su whimpering]

21
00:01:33,140 --> 00:01:34,390
[lady] Yes, sweetheart.

22
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:39,060
-[indistinct chattering]
-[kids shouting indistinctly]

23
00:01:39,140 --> 00:01:40,100
Yun-a.

24
00:01:40,180 --> 00:01:42,270
Oh, no. Be careful.

25
00:01:44,060 --> 00:01:45,560
You should watch where you're going.

26
00:01:48,570 --> 00:01:50,570
[Mr. Lee] <i>Could you let your child die?</i>

27
00:01:53,570 --> 00:01:55,620
No parent on Earth could do that.

28
00:01:55,700 --> 00:01:58,200
I don't wanna hear that bullshit.
Just answer the question.

29
00:01:59,950 --> 00:02:01,250
[Jae-ik] What is the virus and how--

30
00:02:01,330 --> 00:02:03,170
Jae-ik. Code red.

31
00:02:03,250 --> 00:02:05,750
Chief needs everyone right now.
Come on, hurry.

32
00:02:06,380 --> 00:02:07,630
It's too late.

33
00:02:10,670 --> 00:02:11,720
We're all dead.

34
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,430
There's no hope for survival.

35
00:02:15,850 --> 00:02:16,720
[foreboding music playing]

36
00:02:19,010 --> 00:02:20,680
[breathes nervously]

37
00:02:25,860 --> 00:02:26,900
[screaming in distance]

38
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,320
[grunts]

39
00:02:32,780 --> 00:02:33,700
[breathes heavily]

40
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:40,120
Oh, shit.

41
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:42,580
[breathes heavily]

42
00:02:45,250 --> 00:02:46,670
[zombies growling]

43
00:02:49,590 --> 00:02:51,050
[theme music playing]

44
00:03:09,650 --> 00:03:11,860
-[Cheong-san grunts]
-[growling]

45
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,660
Cheong-san!

46
00:03:16,740 --> 00:03:18,320
Look down. Down, down, down.

47
00:03:18,410 --> 00:03:19,620
[growling]

48
00:03:19,700 --> 00:03:20,620
I know.

49
00:03:20,700 --> 00:03:22,950
She's got your foot, moron. Look!

50
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:25,540
-[Cheong-san] I see that.
-Kick her off or something, idiot.

51
00:03:25,620 --> 00:03:26,920
[Cheong-san] I'm trying.

52
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:29,040
[zombie growling]

53
00:03:30,380 --> 00:03:32,000
What the hell is it taking you so long?

54
00:03:32,710 --> 00:03:33,960
[zombie growling]

55
00:03:34,050 --> 00:03:35,380
[Cheong-san grunting]

56
00:03:37,050 --> 00:03:38,220
[gasps]

57
00:03:38,300 --> 00:03:39,550
Hey!

58
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:43,350
Hey. I'm coming down.

59
00:03:44,770 --> 00:03:46,230
No, stay there.

60
00:03:46,310 --> 00:03:48,230
-[grunts]
-No. I said, don't do it.

61
00:03:48,810 --> 00:03:50,440
-I'm coming.
-Don't!

62
00:03:52,190 --> 00:03:54,070
-[Cheong-san] Stay there.
-[Su-hyeok] Oh, shit.

63
00:03:59,110 --> 00:03:59,950
[gasps]
Hold on.

64
00:04:01,780 --> 00:04:03,240
Hey, Bare-su, look up.

65
00:04:05,580 --> 00:04:07,670
[growling]

66
00:04:10,170 --> 00:04:11,380
[grunts]

67
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:13,210
[both grunting, panting]

68
00:04:17,630 --> 00:04:19,680
[zombie growling]

69
00:04:21,390 --> 00:04:23,220
[groaning]
My back.

70
00:04:23,310 --> 00:04:25,770
Just stay still. I'm helping.

71
00:04:26,730 --> 00:04:27,560
[both grunting]

72
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:29,270
[groans]
What are you doing?

73
00:04:30,270 --> 00:04:31,770
-Hold on, moron.
-[grunts]

74
00:04:33,110 --> 00:04:34,980
-[Su-hyeok grunting]
-[zombie growling]

75
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:40,780
-Guys, look, Bare-su. Bare-su!
-Cheong-san!

76
00:04:42,070 --> 00:04:43,330
[zombie shrieks]

77
00:04:45,660 --> 00:04:47,330
Hang on, Bare-su!

78
00:04:47,410 --> 00:04:48,830
Are you okay?

79
00:04:48,910 --> 00:04:49,830
[panting]

80
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:52,540
Shit. Why can't you just kick her…
[panting]

81
00:04:53,340 --> 00:04:54,460
…like I said?

82
00:04:55,050 --> 00:04:57,210
Hey. Stop hugging me.

83
00:04:58,550 --> 00:05:00,010
[Su-hyeok] I'm not hugging you.

84
00:05:01,050 --> 00:05:02,930
[both panting]

85
00:05:03,010 --> 00:05:04,180
Fuck off.

86
00:05:04,260 --> 00:05:05,350
[both laugh]

87
00:05:05,430 --> 00:05:06,470
You like it?

88
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,810
[both laugh]

89
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:11,980
-[Wu-jin] Are you okay?
-[Na-yeon] Close it.

90
00:05:12,060 --> 00:05:14,110
Close it before they get in!

91
00:05:15,270 --> 00:05:17,570
[grumbles, whines]
Would you just close it already?

92
00:05:17,650 --> 00:05:19,450
What's wrong with you?
Cheong-san still out there.

93
00:05:19,530 --> 00:05:20,950
You want us just to shut him out?

94
00:05:21,030 --> 00:05:23,240
Is it a crime to want the window close?

95
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:24,830
How can you be so selfish?

96
00:05:24,910 --> 00:05:25,740
[sighs]

97
00:05:25,830 --> 00:05:27,330
I can't stand you, stupid welfie.

98
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:31,210
[sighs]

99
00:05:32,620 --> 00:05:33,830
[yelps]

100
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,960
-What did you just call me?
-Hey, come on.

101
00:05:36,050 --> 00:05:37,170
What's happening?

102
00:05:37,250 --> 00:05:39,090
-You just hit me?
-Yeah.

103
00:05:39,590 --> 00:05:40,720
Call me that again.

104
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:42,930
Hey, knock it off.
What's going on over here, guys?

105
00:05:43,010 --> 00:05:44,300
He just hit me.

106
00:05:44,390 --> 00:05:46,100
Only 'cause you called me a welfie.

107
00:05:46,180 --> 00:05:48,970
-Is it not true?
-You just can't say shit like that.

108
00:05:49,890 --> 00:05:50,730
What's a welfie?

109
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,480
[Ms. Park] Tell me.

110
00:05:53,060 --> 00:05:54,190
What is it?

111
00:05:57,110 --> 00:05:58,230
What's a welfie?

112
00:06:01,450 --> 00:06:02,820
A person on welfare.

113
00:06:03,660 --> 00:06:06,490
-What?
-It means, a person on welfare.

114
00:06:07,030 --> 00:06:08,910
"Welfie" for short.

115
00:06:09,580 --> 00:06:10,410
[sighs]

116
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:12,960
[sighs]

117
00:06:13,670 --> 00:06:16,590
Na-yeon, that was wrong.
Don't ever say that again.

118
00:06:16,670 --> 00:06:17,750
And Gyeong-su.

119
00:06:17,840 --> 00:06:19,710
When you hit people,
you're the one who ends up losing.

120
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:22,300
-Do you understand?
-No, I don't.

121
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:25,220
Listen, we can't be fighting
each other in a moment like this.

122
00:06:25,300 --> 00:06:26,930
We don't know what's going on
out there with those--

123
00:06:27,010 --> 00:06:28,100
Are they zombies?

124
00:06:29,100 --> 00:06:30,390
What about the other teachers?

125
00:06:30,470 --> 00:06:32,060
Has anyone called the cops?

126
00:06:32,140 --> 00:06:34,270
Don't worry, I'm sure someone already has.

127
00:06:34,350 --> 00:06:35,980
I just don't have
my phone on me, right now.

128
00:06:36,060 --> 00:06:37,900
We called them, but they're not coming.

129
00:06:37,980 --> 00:06:40,570
Neither the police nor first responders.

130
00:06:40,650 --> 00:06:43,360
I'm sure they'll be here soon.
We just have to wait a little longer.

131
00:06:43,450 --> 00:06:46,120
Ms. Park. Hyeon-ju's hands were cold too.

132
00:06:46,870 --> 00:06:48,030
[On-jo] So were I-sak's.

133
00:06:48,530 --> 00:06:50,990
What if all of this started with Hyeon-ju?

134
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:52,750
She went to the hospital.

135
00:06:52,830 --> 00:06:55,370
What if it spread in there as well?

136
00:06:55,460 --> 00:06:57,460
[Hyo-ryeong sighs]
Maybe that's why no one's coming.

137
00:06:57,540 --> 00:07:00,590
But wait. They still work, right?

138
00:07:00,670 --> 00:07:02,340
Uh, internet. The internet.

139
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:04,630
-Let's see. Sorry, Ms. Park.
-Oh.

140
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:06,390
-[Dae-su] Here. Sit.
-[Joon-yeong] Thanks.

141
00:07:07,470 --> 00:07:09,140
[Wu-jin] It should work. Is it on?

142
00:07:09,220 --> 00:07:10,310
[Joon-yeong] I think so.

143
00:07:10,890 --> 00:07:12,560
What's the problem?
Why is it not turning on?

144
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:14,060
-It just did.
-Oh, sorry.

145
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:16,560
[Joon-yeong sighs]
School ones are so slow.

146
00:07:19,150 --> 00:07:20,730
[Wu-jin] Maybe it's not online?

147
00:07:20,820 --> 00:07:22,190
[Joon-yeong] It must be.

148
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:23,740
[Wu-jin sighs]
It's gonna take all day.

149
00:07:23,820 --> 00:07:25,110
[Ji-min] Is it still loading?

150
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:27,110
-Su-hyeok, did you see it?
-[Wu-jin] I don't think it's working.

151
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:28,160
What?

152
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,370
In the science lab.

153
00:07:29,450 --> 00:07:30,660
[zombies growling]

154
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:34,120
SU-HYEOK, WE'RE IN THE
BROADCASTING ROOM - NAM-RA

155
00:07:34,710 --> 00:07:36,330
Well, I was actually in the art room.

156
00:07:37,540 --> 00:07:39,040
-[boys chattering]
-What's in the science lab?

157
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:41,590
Uh, well…

158
00:07:41,670 --> 00:07:43,260
-[computer chimes]
-[Joon-yeong] It worked.

159
00:07:44,010 --> 00:07:46,510
-Okay. Open the browser.
-[Dae-su] The browser.

160
00:07:46,590 --> 00:07:47,760
[computer whirring]

161
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:49,680
[Dae-su] Look up "zombie virus."

162
00:07:49,760 --> 00:07:50,720
[window clanks]

163
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:52,180
-[Wu-jin] Yeah, "zombie virus."
-[Ji-min] But…

164
00:07:52,260 --> 00:07:54,680
-[Hyo-ryeong] No. Try "Hyosan."
-[Ji-min] See what's trending.

165
00:07:54,770 --> 00:07:56,020
-[Joon-yeong] No.
-[Ji-min sighs in annoyance]

166
00:07:56,100 --> 00:07:57,940
-I'm checking the news first.
-Look up the emergence alerts.

167
00:07:58,020 --> 00:07:59,270
-[Wu-jin] The news.
-[Dae-su] There'll be no articles yet.

168
00:07:59,350 --> 00:08:01,360
-[Cheong-san] Yeah, go to the news.
-[Hyo-ryeong] What are we looking up?

169
00:08:02,980 --> 00:08:03,860
[brake squeals]

170
00:08:04,940 --> 00:08:05,900
[woman 1] See you later.

171
00:08:09,320 --> 00:08:10,620
[car whooshes]

172
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,290
[tires screeching]

173
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,040
[car honking]

174
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,330
[tire whirring]

175
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:24,170
-Are you okay? Let me help you.
-Come on.

176
00:08:24,250 --> 00:08:25,590
Stand up. Can you stand?

177
00:08:26,970 --> 00:08:29,800
-[woman 2] Call an ambulance.
-[man 1] Let's get out of the way first.

178
00:08:29,890 --> 00:08:31,220
-See that?
-What's going on?

179
00:08:31,300 --> 00:08:32,550
[police officer 1 grunting]

180
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:35,640
-[breathing heavily, gasping]
-[retches]

181
00:08:36,140 --> 00:08:38,980
Sir, are you all right? Do you need help?

182
00:08:39,690 --> 00:08:41,270
-[zombie snarls]
-[man 2 screaming]

183
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:42,560
[tense music playing]

184
00:08:42,650 --> 00:08:44,070
-[zombie growling]
-[screaming]

185
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:46,530
[munching, growling]

186
00:08:47,650 --> 00:08:49,240
[whimpering]

187
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,160
[growls]

188
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,620
Oh, shit.

189
00:08:54,700 --> 00:08:55,740
[pants]

190
00:08:56,660 --> 00:08:58,330
[growling]

191
00:08:58,910 --> 00:08:59,750
[snarls]

192
00:09:00,920 --> 00:09:02,920
[growls, screams]

193
00:09:03,460 --> 00:09:04,880
[groans]

194
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:05,920
No. No, please!

195
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:07,970
[breathing heavily]

196
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:13,680
[breathing heavily]

197
00:09:15,220 --> 00:09:16,720
[growls]

198
00:09:17,430 --> 00:09:18,730
[grunting]

199
00:09:21,020 --> 00:09:22,440
[clamoring]

200
00:09:24,230 --> 00:09:26,530
[screaming in distance]

201
00:09:28,740 --> 00:09:29,610
I'll try Facebook.

202
00:09:32,160 --> 00:09:32,990
[keyboard clacking]

203
00:09:33,070 --> 00:09:34,410
Or Instagram.

204
00:09:34,490 --> 00:09:35,870
Do you have followers?

205
00:09:35,950 --> 00:09:37,120
Let's do Facebook.

206
00:09:37,740 --> 00:09:38,950
Hmm…

207
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,750
-[notification chimes]
-Okay.

208
00:09:44,330 --> 00:09:46,000
How many friends do you have?

209
00:09:46,090 --> 00:09:48,090
[Dae-su] Look at your notifications.1,700?

210
00:09:49,300 --> 00:09:50,670
Strange.

211
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:53,890
Okay, let's check messages first.

212
00:09:55,220 --> 00:09:56,930
[all clamoring]

213
00:09:57,760 --> 00:09:59,390
-[Joon-yeong] What the hell?
-Oh, shit.

214
00:09:59,470 --> 00:10:00,480
[suspenseful music playing]

215
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:01,810
[groaning]

216
00:10:01,890 --> 00:10:03,600
-[Joon-yeong] What was that?
-[flustered murmur]

217
00:10:03,690 --> 00:10:04,810
[Ms. Park] Get over here. Come here.

218
00:10:06,230 --> 00:10:07,570
Did someone not make it in?

219
00:10:08,690 --> 00:10:10,110
No. No one.

220
00:10:12,700 --> 00:10:13,910
Wait. Don't go too close!

221
00:10:13,990 --> 00:10:14,990
Cheong-san.

222
00:10:15,820 --> 00:10:16,910
Be careful.

223
00:10:17,580 --> 00:10:19,290
[glass shattering]

224
00:10:23,420 --> 00:10:24,580
Do you see anything?

225
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,010
It's just the wind.

226
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:33,800
[Wu-jin] That scared me.

227
00:10:34,300 --> 00:10:36,510
-[growls]
-[all gasps, clamoring]

228
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:38,100
[screaming]

229
00:10:39,510 --> 00:10:41,140
Look, it's coming in!
Watch out, watch out!

230
00:10:41,730 --> 00:10:42,600
[zombie growling]

231
00:10:43,100 --> 00:10:45,020
Cheong-san, get back. Get back here.

232
00:10:45,100 --> 00:10:45,980
[snarling]

233
00:10:46,060 --> 00:10:47,520
[Gyeong-su] Look out, look out!

234
00:10:49,070 --> 00:10:50,110
[Ms. Park] Cheong-san!

235
00:10:51,110 --> 00:10:52,740
-Cheong-san!
-Get back here!

236
00:10:52,820 --> 00:10:54,030
[Dae-su] Wait. w-w-wait, wait!

237
00:10:54,110 --> 00:10:55,740
-[growling]
-[grunts]

238
00:10:55,820 --> 00:10:58,240
-[Su-hyeok] Push it! Push it off.
-[Dae-su] Did you get it?

239
00:10:58,330 --> 00:10:59,370
-[zombie growling]
-Push it!

240
00:10:59,450 --> 00:11:00,540
-[grunts]
-[Gyeong-su] Push it off.

241
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:03,830
[Gyeong-su] Push it off!

242
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:06,170
[Gyeong-su] Push it! Come on.

243
00:11:06,790 --> 00:11:07,960
Go! Harder!

244
00:11:08,040 --> 00:11:09,250
[growling]

245
00:11:10,880 --> 00:11:12,130
-Watch out!
-Remove her hand!

246
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:15,180
[groaning]
Shit!

247
00:11:15,970 --> 00:11:17,300
-[screaming]
-Stay back!

248
00:11:21,260 --> 00:11:22,470
-[grunts]
-[all gasp]

249
00:11:25,020 --> 00:11:26,270
[zombie growling]

250
00:11:27,350 --> 00:11:28,560
[zombie snarling]

251
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,820
[Na-yeon] Don't go near it!

252
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:35,610
-Should I go?
-Stay back.

253
00:11:35,700 --> 00:11:37,450
No. Hold on.

254
00:11:37,530 --> 00:11:38,820
-[Su-hyeok] Go, Dae-su.
-[growls]

255
00:11:38,910 --> 00:11:39,910
[snarling]

256
00:11:41,660 --> 00:11:42,990
-Give me.
-[growling]

257
00:11:43,950 --> 00:11:45,120
[grunts]

258
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:49,000
[breathing heavily]

259
00:11:53,420 --> 00:11:54,670
[growling]

260
00:11:55,800 --> 00:11:56,880
[snarls]

