276
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:34,920
[sighs]

277
00:12:35,010 --> 00:12:37,090
-[Cheong-san] Are you okay?
-[Gyeong-su] Yeah, I'm good.

278
00:12:39,590 --> 00:12:40,550
