280
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:50,650
Hey.

281
00:12:51,810 --> 00:12:52,650
[Na-yeon] You…

282
00:12:57,030 --> 00:12:58,740
RESCUE

283
00:12:58,820 --> 00:13:01,700
HYOSAN CITY COUNCIL

284
00:13:02,740 --> 00:13:03,620
[groaning]

285
00:13:04,780 --> 00:13:07,370
You have to understand
