286
00:13:07,450 --> 00:13:10,580
When he got back from the Council building
he just collapsed and started convulsing.

287
00:13:10,670 --> 00:13:14,590
-[croaks]
-Captain. He smells like a rotting corpse.

288
00:13:14,670 --> 00:13:16,460
And then he got back up, and went like…

289
00:13:16,550 --> 00:13:17,380
[imitates growling]

290
00:13:17,460 --> 00:13:19,630
