out of nowhere.

291
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:21,260
[sighs]
So we tied him up to that chair.

292
00:13:21,340 --> 00:13:23,850
But we didn't know
if we should call the police. You know?

293
00:13:23,930 --> 00:13:25,010
Why are you telling them that?

294
00:13:25,760 --> 00:13:27,270
-[croaks]
-He'll bite his tongue.

295
00:13:28,100 --> 00:13:29,730
-We have to gag him.
-Copy.

296
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:34,270
[growls]

297
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:35,480
-Ready?
-Yes.

298
00:13:35,980 --> 00:13:38,400
One, two, three.

299
00:13:38,490 --> 00:13:39,650
[growling]

300
00:13:40,900 --> 00:13:41,780
[grunts]

301
00:13:41,860 --> 00:13:44,200
-Did it get you?
-It's okay. A little.

302
00:13:44,280 --> 00:13:45,280
Wrap him up!

303
00:13:46,330 --> 00:13:47,160
Now.

304
00:13:47,950 --> 00:13:49,660
-[muffled growls]
-[grunting]

