that happened to I-sak.

338
00:15:12,200 --> 00:15:13,410
Gyeong-su.

339
00:15:13,500 --> 00:15:15,620
[splutters]
I-I'm telling you! I swear I wasn't bit!

340
00:15:19,250 --> 00:15:20,670
[sighs in annoyance]
Shit.

341
00:15:20,750 --> 00:15:22,130
Look.

342
00:15:22,210 --> 00:15:24,630
Your hand. Explain that?

343
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:26,050
What is it?

344
00:15:27,970 --> 00:15:30,060
I got it from the computer.
Didn't you see that?

345
00:15:30,140 --> 00:15:31,010
[all gasp]

346
00:15:32,470 --> 00:15:33,520
[scoffs]

347
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:34,770
Don't you trust me?

348
00:15:35,730 --> 00:15:38,980
I can't believe this.
I got this trying to save all of you.

349
00:15:40,110 --> 00:15:40,940
[Gyeong-su hisses]

350
00:15:45,610 --> 00:15:47,700
It's not a bite. It's a scratch.

351
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:50,080
Whoever wants to check, come look.

352
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:53,410
[Dae-su] It's a scratch?

353
00:15:54,410 --> 00:15:56,830
Yeah, definitely. Just a scratch.

354
00:15:57,420 --> 00:15:59,000
-Ms. Park, look.
-Mm.

355
00:16:00,540 --> 00:16:03,510
Well, it really doesn't look like a bite.
Thank god. It's a scratch.

356
00:16:03,590 --> 00:16:05,090
He's okay.

357
00:16:09,800 --> 00:16:10,720
Done yet?

358
00:16:11,810 --> 00:16:13,470
