359
00:16:14,560 --> 00:16:18,190
Wait. This means the computer's gone.

360
00:16:18,270 --> 00:16:19,400
No internet…

361
00:16:20,650 --> 00:16:22,820
Couldn't you have thrown something else
instead of the computer?

362
00:16:22,900 --> 00:16:24,860
What was I supposed to do?
It's trying to get in.

363
00:16:25,490 --> 00:16:28,780
No, you did good. Thank you. Don't be mad.

364
00:16:29,780 --> 00:16:31,070
Hey, Na-yeon.

365
00:16:31,160 --> 00:16:33,580
Look. Say sorry. End this.

366
00:16:34,160 --> 00:16:35,410
