367
00:16:35,500 --> 00:16:37,370
[scoffs]
He did it to save us all.

368
00:16:37,460 --> 00:16:39,040
Why can't you just say that you're sorry?

369
00:16:39,120 --> 00:16:40,630
Because I'm not sorry.

370
00:16:41,710 --> 00:16:43,000
I saw everything.

371
00:16:43,090 --> 00:16:44,300
I saw the creature grabbed you.

372
00:16:44,380 --> 00:16:45,670
[zombie growling]

373
00:16:47,720 --> 00:16:49,010
[Na-yeon] <i>I'm right.</i>

374
00:16:49,680 --> 00:16:50,840
He could be infected.

375
00:16:50,930 --> 00:16:52,390
Na-yeon, enough.

376
00:16:52,470 --> 00:16:54,560
It really did.
That thing grabbed his hand.

377
00:16:55,560 --> 00:16:57,640
Wait, can touching his hand infect him?

378
00:16:57,730 --> 00:16:59,190
I have no idea but maybe.

379
00:16:59,270 --> 00:17:01,310
I held I-sak's hand when she fell.

380
00:17:02,060 --> 00:17:03,150
Why is nothing happening to me?

381
00:17:03,230 --> 00:17:05,030
Because he has a cut on his hand.

382
00:17:05,110 --> 00:17:07,610
