it's probably gonna be different.

383
00:17:07,690 --> 00:17:08,990
-That's fucking--
-Don't.

384
00:17:09,070 --> 00:17:11,700
Stop blaming me.
Why don't you just think for yourselves?

385
00:17:11,780 --> 00:17:12,620
[Gyeong-su sighs]

386
00:17:13,320 --> 00:17:14,240
Na-yeon.

387
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:17,500
I know you always hated Gyeong-su,

388
00:17:17,580 --> 00:17:19,620
