the line here.

389
00:17:19,710 --> 00:17:21,330
This is about life and death.

390
00:17:21,420 --> 00:17:22,750
She's always like this.

391
00:17:23,250 --> 00:17:24,210
[scoffs]

392
00:17:24,290 --> 00:17:27,090
If it weren't for him,
we would definitely all be dead right now.

393
00:17:27,170 --> 00:17:29,470
And now, he might be the one
killing all of us.

394
00:17:29,550 --> 00:17:31,260
Now you're the one who's killing me.

395
00:17:31,340 --> 00:17:32,760
-Just shut up, Na-yeon.
-Look at my hand, I'm totally fine.

396
00:17:32,840 --> 00:17:34,680
-Don't you see that?
-Hey, that's enough, all of you! Okay?

397
00:17:34,760 --> 00:17:35,600
We're ending this.

398
00:17:35,680 --> 00:17:36,890
-Ms. Park--
-Enough.

399
00:17:36,970 --> 00:17:37,930
-But she--
-No!

400
00:17:39,560 --> 00:17:40,730
[sighs]

401
00:17:45,150 --> 00:17:46,070
[sighs]

402
00:17:47,570 --> 00:17:48,650
Let's do this.

403
00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:52,700
Gyeong-su, you're going to wait
in the recording room for ten minutes.

404
00:17:52,780 --> 00:17:53,990
I know it'll be hard,

405
00:17:54,070 --> 00:17:56,240
but at least it's better
than people thinking you're infected.

406
00:17:56,330 --> 00:17:59,500
No one else thinks that I'm infected.
It's only her.

407
00:17:59,580 --> 00:18:02,370
Gyeong-su, would you please do it?

408
00:18:04,750 --> 00:18:06,540
Fuck ten. I'll do half…

409
00:18:07,050 --> 00:18:08,550
I'll just do a full hour.

410
00:18:08,630 --> 00:18:12,010
There's really no point doing an hour
since it takes less than five minutes.

411
00:18:12,090 --> 00:18:13,760
-Stop overreacting.
-It's just to be sure.

412
00:18:15,430 --> 00:18:16,510
[Ms. Park] Is that enough?

413
00:18:18,060 --> 00:18:20,430
And if nothing happens,
you'll apologize, right?

414
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:23,350
Yeah.

415
00:18:24,650 --> 00:18:27,480
And everyone else
is okay with that, right?

416
00:18:27,570 --> 00:18:28,780
[all] Yes.

417
00:18:29,690 --> 00:18:32,400
If we do this,
who's gonna step up next time?

418
00:18:32,490 --> 00:18:33,820
We all be too scared.

419
00:18:35,070 --> 00:18:36,450
You're right, but…

420
00:18:39,870 --> 00:18:42,830
Let's consider this a way
to learn to trust each other.

421
00:18:45,330 --> 00:18:48,170
I do… trust Gyeong-su.

422
00:18:52,760 --> 00:18:53,930
See you in an hour.

423
00:18:55,800 --> 00:18:57,050
Want me to come with you?

424
00:19:07,650 --> 00:19:09,070
[Dae-su] What a stubborn asshole.

425
00:19:09,940 --> 00:19:11,230
He only needs to do ten.

426
00:19:11,320 --> 00:19:12,610
He's not that stubborn.

427
00:19:13,280 --> 00:19:14,400
Compared to her.

428
00:19:14,490 --> 00:19:15,860
[sighs]

429
00:19:21,950 --> 00:19:23,750
