431
00:19:34,670 --> 00:19:37,010
-Go get it.
-No. I won't.

432
00:19:37,090 --> 00:19:38,090
You stupid little…

433
00:19:38,600 --> 00:19:39,470
Stop. Please.

434
00:19:39,550 --> 00:19:41,140
-Go, asshole.
-[grunts]

